{"tid":1616253,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"譚文豪獲撤銷阻差辦公罪","createTime":"2019-10-03T10:33:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T10:59:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"50f5690ae06685030d81ba0d94e47f9ed9175180","tid":1616253,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:33:23.000Z","msg":"【撤銷阻差辦公罪】 #律政司指不恰當起訴<br />\n<br />\n今日我與區諾軒議員到警署續保時，獲警方通知撤銷控告阻差辦公，律政司指相關罪名屬不恰當起訴。<br />\n<br />\n其實早於7月中我已經就員佐級協會發聲明指「議員阻差辦公」時，已借2005年《談立徽案》法庭判辭指出，單單與警察理論、糾正警察的錯誤不構成阻差辦公！今次律政司正正摑員佐級協會響亮一巴掌，同時證明議員有權力在前線行使監察權，糾正警察錯誤，警察不應阻撓，甚至隨意恐嚇巿民、指控巿民阻差辦公。<br />\n<br />\n我再次譴責警方於8.31前夕大搜捕，企圖阻嚇巿民表達訴求，完全是政治凌駕公義，將來必因濫捕而付出代價！<br />\n<br />\n另外，區諾軒仍就7.7旺角事件被控兩項襲警罪，將於10月17日上庭。<br />\n<br />\n時任終審法院常任法官陳兆愷在2005年《談立徽》案指出：<br />\n//阻差辦工的「阻礙」，不應是瑣碎、無聊的阻礙；如果當事人只是保障自己權利，例如行使其緘默權而不說話，要求警察澄清所為何事，或者與警察理論，企圖糾正警察的錯誤，或者想保護正被警察查問的親友等，都不構成阻差辦工//"},{"pid":"d0bec64a9a6fd34cc78768f5d857685fb607614b","tid":1616253,"uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:34:02.000Z","msg":"<strong>今次律政司正正摑員佐級協會響亮一巴掌，同時證明議員有權力在前線行使監察權，糾正警察錯誤，警察不應阻撓，甚至隨意恐嚇巿民、指控巿民阻差辦公。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong>"},{"pid":"399fa6cb89aba668af55bee369325e921e0f5c52","tid":1616253,"uid":136747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:34:24.000Z","msg":"「突發」今晚8點葵涌邨商場要人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1616230\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1616230</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <br />\n大家幫手推一推 商場內藍旗 管理處拒絕回應"},{"pid":"620af7d89cf750c9468f63dd8e1b2d5fc621392a","tid":1616253,"uid":38109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f7deec073dd124e268ec3ceb5c62035499493a7","tid":1616253,"uid":1550,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:35:16.000Z","msg":"等睇散仔屌律政司"},{"pid":"f5219ebd211bfa75b59bf0a4b6eb8035d9ad1225","tid":1616253,"uid":111006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:36:36.000Z","msg":"係咪可以出返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b574bafaf1ff50e556b2b736270a8af26c1c4480","tid":1616253,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1f7deec073dd124e268ec3ceb5c62035499493a7","tid":1616253,"uid":1550,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:35:16.000Z","msg":"等睇散仔屌律政司"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:36:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de036fab087b0f621689ca68dd4572781120d584","tid":1616253,"uid":70988,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:37:05.000Z","msg":"條撚樣投左誠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a419810c4bf0e1ace966b9f21c7b6216cc392a","tid":1616253,"uid":1430,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f7deec073dd124e268ec3ceb5c62035499493a7","tid":1616253,"uid":1550,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:35:16.000Z","msg":"等睇散仔屌律政司"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:37:11.000Z","msg":"林大總統叫大波嬅出黎露出胸部道歉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a9ab94d15a3db6fd12052033068de483a6d0b5","tid":1616253,"uid":70988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:38:55.000Z","msg":"據《文匯報》今日（9月27日）報道，公民黨立法會議員譚文豪表示，自己並沒有利用飛機上的廣播系統，宣傳「反修例」活動，因他自2016年當選立法會議員後已沒有飛，自言肯定與事件無關。 《文匯報》刊出一篇專訪，內容提到譚文豪強調自己是「和理非」，對暴力感到心痛，「我相信沒有香港人會希望見到暴力的出現，不希望見到有人受傷、打人或有人被打，都不想見到，作為香港人，見到這樣的情況一定會很心痛。」被問到會想對暴力分子說些什麼，他說︰「不要危及普通市民的安全，一些不打算參與示威的人或會受到威脅，這是一個大問題。」 譚文豪認為，自己既是香港人，也是中國人，不支持「港獨」。他說，現在問題是「一國兩制」在設計時未能預視幾十年後的問題，故要回到初衷，並要為香港市民、特區政府和中央政府重建互信，多作溝通。<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"https://www.passiontimes.hk/article/09-27-2019/56242\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F09-27-2019%2F56242&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEtqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=b1466662\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.passiontimes.hk/article/09-27-2019/56242</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2019"},{"pid":"8e8a43af90abd03e86c48e2e6a476c1ffbac4f13","tid":1616253,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:54:08.000Z","msg":"係撚律政司正正摑員佐級協會響亮一巴掌<br />\n<br />\n刑事檢控專員咪共狗<br />\n條友都知自己個名比人交左比美國, 準備奶美國春袋搏平安"},{"pid":"5b8414fe7b0706b7d974807121b4ef37842dcde9","tid":1616253,"uid":301507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:59:47.000Z","msg":"吿返警務處長、民事索償啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n精神傷害呀、時間損失呀、計計埋埋陪幾千萬冇走雞，然後捐比星火612嗰啲。"}]}